<p><strong>Challenge</strong> 1 (200 XP)</p>

<p><strong><em>Heated Body.</em></strong> A creature that touches the snake or hits it with a melee attack while within 5 ft. of it takes 3 (1d6) fire damage.</p>

<p><strong>Actions</strong></p>

<p><strong><em>Multiattack.</em></strong> The snake makes two attacks: one with its bite and one with its tail.</p>

<p><strong><em>Bite.</em></strong> Melee Weapon Attack: +3 to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. Hit: 3 (1d4 + 1) piercing damage plus 3 (1d6) fire damage.</p>

<p><strong><em>Tail.</em></strong> Melee Weapon Attack: +3 to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. Hit: 3 (1d4 + 1) bludgeoning damage plus 3 (1d6) fire damage.</p>

